,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:26:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">816，星期五</span></span>，請將所有銀行存款從銀行中提走，記住是提走或匯到離岸戶口，而非從一間銀行轉到另一間銀行，並將MPF組合全部轉成非香港及中國資產。<br />\n<br />\n雖然機場實施管制，但我們可以利用自己鈔票的力量，表明我們對現任政府已經失去信心。<br />\n<br />\n香港銀行體系結餘只有五百多億，如果二百萬人每人提走$25,000，已經能夠令結餘歸零。之後，就讓信用塌縮完成餘下的工作。"},{"pid":"9f4bd038032fc2e2d9737f289e8a07ef10c239a4","tid":1471652,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:27:17.000Z","msg":"816"},{"pid":"be710f0fd49f24c7b33ef6fc431c578ef3cd433e","tid":1471652,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:27:28.000Z","msg":"816"},{"pid":"f07b06020bf163e044517e7a4d38dcc1d99572e1","tid":1471652,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:27:46.000Z","msg":"816"},{"pid":"5ff24fd61abad7d7eda99e8632ff5002dffaa95e","tid":1471652,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:27:59.000Z","msg":"816"},{"pid":"0b5782706bbb4a35777eb6767ef797e762edb5af","tid":1471652,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"816"},{"pid":"579dc829ba3d7866a51b44e3ecf77c899b062c5a","tid":1471652,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:28:29.000Z","msg":"816"},{"pid":"90a5feec5ddac78a3b6d59b6629395abf62f8529","tid":1471652,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:29:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9699a3d2e489073b7d4bb43749bc1f884e8cbea","tid":1471652,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:29:54.000Z","msg":"Push &amp; 借位 post<br />\n<br />\n（尋失物) 今日13/8 喺機場唔見咗個背囊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n緊急 8月5號 深水埗 有冇手足執到？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470195